### Test Tasks API with Frontend Parameters

### 1. Login first to get token
POST http://localhost:3000/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "user@example.com",
  "password": "user123"
}

### 2. Test tasks endpoint with frontend parameters
GET http://localhost:3000/api/tasks?scope=my&status=todo&priority=high&q=test&sortBy=createdAt&sortOrder=desc&limit=20
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

### 3. Test with tags parameter
GET http://localhost:3000/api/tasks?tags=urgent,important&scope=my
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

### 4. Test with all parameters
GET http://localhost:3000/api/tasks?scope=my&status=in_progress&priority=medium&q=project&sortBy=title&sortOrder=asc&limit=10&cursor=test
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

### 5. Test organization scope (for managers/admins)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/tasks?scope=org&status=done
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE
